channel.title: Need blank server/client [delta-317]
channel.description:
thanks for reading.
i recently gave up on finding a good delta 317 source to code because tbh there arent any. so i need help finding a somewhat blank source and a compatible, editble client
(i know what yerr gona say: delta sux azzzz----TROLLLLLZZZZZ,,, har-de-har-har-har, flamefuck, fuckflame)
the kind of client/source i need: - all working 317 items - preferably no customs (except gs's, spirit shields, ect... if already in the client) - no pre-existing shops - working pvp - working default NPC's (slayer tower, jad, corp, GDW, other standard NPC's) - 1000000% working Special attacks - all working skills - dueling - some minigames, assault, pits, pest control (if possible)
basically if you find a good working clean, blank client or source, post here
